        <updateDate>2015-06-24T13:55:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Protecting Taxpayers and Communities from Local Detention Quotas Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement from negotiating a contract with a private detention company that contains any provision relating to a guaranteed minimum number of immigration detention beds at any specific facility. </p> <p>This prohibition also applies to a contract extension or contract renegotiation.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Protecting Taxpayers and Communities from Local Detention Quotas Act</title>
    <titles>
